body:
Day 18:

This is my gift for the amazing @liusyss ! Their art was always amazing ever since I came across them but now that I keep thinking their art is canon, I’m always left speechless. Not just canon-like art, but it seems like everyone they post something new, they know just how to surprise me.

Your art is too powerful, Liusyss. And I’m here for it. 💕 I hope you like it!

Merry Countdown to Christmas! 🎄❄️

summary: dabi was fully and entirely prepared to kill endeavor on national live television. the only reason he backed out was because...
body:
dabi was fully and entirely prepared to kill endeavor on national live television. the only reason he backed out was because miruko, who has a strength-enhancing quirk, showed up and called him out.

conclusion? dabi is a weak bitch who can’t throw a decent punch to save his gotdam life and will run away the second you’re within less than 12 feet of him.
